{"tid":1475112,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[還原真相]811爆門牙義士原來係比疑似公安用警棍插頭","createTime":"2019-08-15T11:16:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T16:12:01.000Z","uid":95407,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"29255cc722b6e849952072bfa184701609a5e225","tid":1475112,"uid":95407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"睇返呢段Guardian既新聞片段(0:25秒)清楚影到有警棍, 由個刁鑽既角度打左義士個頭兩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ekLUcW-HVMw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FekLUcW-HVMw&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=deea51c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ekLUcW-HVMw</a><br />\n<br />\n再睇返Facebook有人share, 話防暴警用普通話+鄉音廣東話叫人退後一點, 退後D<br />\n原來同打義士頭既防暴警係同一條友!!!!!!!!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋根本唔係單純打落頭到 (雖然都賤到仆街) 而係由下而上插向義士個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1:14秒防暴公安用警棍篤落義士頭部 ; 1:50秒防暴公安唔小心講左普通話<br />\n片中記者相信就係Guardian記者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/maxngck/videos/10157404126951870/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmaxngck%2Fvideos%2F10157404126951870%2F&d=LSsgDEuqvL%2F6lC7PehFbgxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=1374dd70\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/maxngck/videos/10157404126951870/</a><br />\n<br />\n各位睇清楚, 果兩棍係由義士下巴, 從下而上插向佢個頭, 根本係想致人嚴重傷害, 甚至致命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前都有習武巴打留言, 話警棍/棍狀武器毆落人到, 同篤落人到個痛楚同傷害係完全兩個程度<br />\n<br />\n利申返: 整合返件事唔係想幫黑警洗白, 點撚洗都唔甩架啦, 呢單野證明左混入狗隊既公安, 使用極端暴力參與鎮壓義士, 更加令香港人髮指<br />\n<br />\n希望各位提供唔同角度既片, 加以引證<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"785a0accb68e1379b41dd2b1f760c9b205dfdb3e","tid":1475112,"uid":95407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:18:45.000Z","msg":"自推1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3834f8f137f4259485a3f0964a25f5add07d808b","tid":1475112,"uid":95407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:19:32.000Z","msg":"自推2<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3b1b1c25c257df2116585da07cb21eda4f419c5","tid":1475112,"uid":95407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"自推3<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dd7f40a2d696ea5cdb5f33fba1345007b767fad","tid":1475112,"uid":95407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:21:42.000Z","msg":"自推4<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16a2201aec8dbe18112a44b81827fd9e48ec1e67","tid":1475112,"uid":73805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:22:54.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"b7cad1e6d464895ba888c553f16d340b3fb248c1","tid":1475112,"uid":95407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T11:23:52.000Z","msg":"自推5<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd5eff60975fe99ceb368b37b5367dcc4d0bf490","tid":1475112,"uid":292901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"推！！！！"},{"pid":"1afda08b6ee827a6670907dd2fd5bcb3c6f4f292","tid":1475112,"uid":292901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"好兇殘嘅手法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr